machette (0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Renamed project from Regex Tool to Machette.
  * Added safe-mode support.
  * Added 'Reference guide' module.
  * Made source code PEP-8 compliant.
  * Made some code cleanup and improvements.

 -- Vincent Batoufflet <vincent@batoufflet.info>  Sat, 09 Oct 2010 17:55:11 +0200

machette (0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added modules support.
  * Added undo/redo support for GtkTextView.
  * Added import/export support for target string.
  * Added selection highlighting support (through a new module).
  * Made configuration handler use ConfigObj instead of ConfigParser.
  * Made some GUI improvements.
  * Fixed various bugs.

 -- Vincent Batoufflet <vincent@batoufflet.info>  Sat, 17 Jul 2010 13:41:24 +0200

machette (0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Release.

